+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01VrQgcTNu5Cc6enHi5fLzF9","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks complete. Here's a summary of what was built:\n\n## Implementation Summary\n\n**5 source files** created in `src/`:\n\n1. **`src/database.ts`** — SQLite database layer using better-sqlite3. Initializes the schema from `schema.sql`, provides `DocumentStore` class with CRUD operations, version history tracking, and content updates with operation logging.\n\n2. **`src/ot.ts`** — Operational Transform engine with:\n   - `InsertOp` and `DeleteOp` operation types\n   - `applyOp()` — applies an operation to document content\n   - `validateOp()` — validates operations against document state\n   - `transformOp()` — transforms concurrent operations (insert-insert, insert-delete, delete-insert, delete-delete) to ensure convergence\n\n3. **`src/routes.ts`** — Express router with REST endpoints:\n   - `POST /documents` — create document\n   - `GET /documents` — list all documents\n   - `GET /documents/:id` — get single document\n   - `PUT /documents/:id` — update document\n   - `DELETE /documents/:id` — delete document\n   - `GET /documents/:id/versions` — get version history\n\n4. **`src/websocket.ts`** — WebSocket collaboration handler:\n   - Connects at `/ws/documents/:id`\n   - Sends `sync` message with current content + version on connect\n   - Receives `operation` messages, transforms against concurrent ops via OT, applies, persists, sends `ack` to sender and broadcasts to other clients\n   - Handles error cases (invalid path, missing document, malformed operations)\n\n5. **`src/server.ts`** — Entry point exporting `createApp(dbPath?)` factory that returns `{ app, start(port?), stop() }`\n\n6. **`src/index.ts`** — Re-exports from server.ts\n\n**3 test files** with 48 tests covering:\n- OT engine (25 tests): apply, validate, transform, convergence proofs\n- REST API (12 tests): full CRUD lifecycle, erro